page_0: "Mr. Boleston,
Here are the figures I mentioned during our chat:

PTR(x)                                      alpha(o)
  175-239-54-785-323-473            115-975-81-322-942-163
SO(l)                                       gamma(f)
  4-8-15-16-23-42                         121-866-22-923-584-367

Might I also suggest adopting these settings to the museum's system if you find the results satisfactory.

It has been a pleasure and inspiration talking to you.

Sincerely,
Marten"
